         <abstract id="aspace_4bc23e7dc131d94bf602fe1266ef375b">On 17 May 1977 the academic year closed with Kingman Brewster, Jr.'s, resignation from office to become ambassador to the Court of St. James under President Jimmy Carter. The records consist of Brewster's handwritten resignation letter, as well as other writings in his honor.</abstract>
