         <p>Kingman Brewster, Jr., President of Yale University, Resignation Records (YRU 14) Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_783495ebf089028fbd7d545d1be6df65">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_6a32df9732472fa3e698cbab094158ce">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>On 17 May 1977 the academic year closed with Kingman Brewster, Jr.'s, resignation from office to become ambassador to the Court of St. James under President Jimmy Carter. The records consist of Brewster's handwritten resignation letter, as well as other writings in his honor.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
